        "text": ": صانع المنافق بلسانك، وأخلص ودك للمؤمن، وإن جالسك يهودي فأحسن مجالسته ."
      },
      "translations": {
        "en.mulla-asgharali-m-m-jaffer": {
          "segments": [
            "10. And with the preceding chains of narration from ‘Ali ibn Mahzyar, from al-Hasan ibn Mahboob, from Muhammad ibn Sinan, from al-Husayn ibn Mas’ab, from Sa’d ibn Turaif, from: Abu Ja’far Muhammad ibn ‘Ali, peace be upon both, who said: \"Soften your speech with [even] the hypocrite, love the faithful believer sincerely, and [even] if a Jew were to sit with you, then be gracious in his company.\""
          ],
          "text": "10. And with the preceding chains of narration from ‘Ali ibn Mahzyar, from al-Hasan ibn Mahboob, from Muhammad ibn Sinan, from al-Husayn ibn Mas’ab, from Sa’d ibn Turaif, from: Abu Ja’far Muhammad ibn ‘Ali, peace be upon both, who said: \"Soften your speech with [even] the hypocrite, love the faithful believer sincerely, and [even] if a Jew were to sit with you, then be gracious in his company.\""
        }
      },
